Jim Jordan (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_Jordan_(actor) 0 James Edward Jordan (November 16, 1896 – April 1, 1988) was the American actor who played Fibber McGee in Fibber McGee and Molly and voiced the albatross Orville in Disney's The Rescuers (1977). James_Edward_Jordan ( November_16_,_1896 – April_1_,_1988 ) was the_American_actor who played Fibber_McGee in Fibber_McGee and Molly and voiced the_albatross Orville in Disney 's_The_Rescuers ( 1977 ) .
